data.description: BEAUTIFUL, custom built WALKOUT RAMBLER backing to wetlands and wildlife! Feel the joy living in one of the most desirable Andover neighborhoods…location, location, location! GORGEOUS gourmet kitchen with large center island, TONS of custom cabinetry with extra tall upper cabinets, tile backsplash and solid wood floors throughout kitchen, dining and foyer (quality, quality, quality!) SPACIOUS dining area leads to FABULOUS 30x16 wrap around deck with composite decking! Light & bright great room with oversized windows and soaring vault. Convenient main floor laundry and mud room. Private primary bath ~ dual sinks and separate tub & shower. FINISHED walkout lower level with huge family room featuring full stone, gas fireplace. Two more bedrooms and a full bathroom too!  Oversized 3 car garage plus 2 sheds.  Walk to Andover schools, YMCA & Community Center. Biking/walking paths to the regional parks. Super clean and meticulously maintained!  BONUS ~ newer roof & siding!
